intervention.description:
Electronic medical records will be reviewed to collect the following data:
Proportion of patients who fits criteria of EOL who died within 48 hours;
Proportion of patients on EOL pathway who have documentation that patient and/or family are given opportunities to discuss an individualised care plan;
Proportion of patients on EOL pathway who have documentation of an individualised care plan that is followed;
Proportion of patients on EOL pathway who have symptoms who are prescribed with medicines with individualised indications for use, dosage and route of administration
